title: Martial Law 911: Rise of the Police State (2005) -- Good Quality
description:
"Martial Law 911" documents the signs of a growing Police State: 

Constant surveillance, a defined military presence, a militarized civilian police force, mass roundups and arrests of protesters, detention in a makeshift facility laden with asbestos which one interviewee called a "concentration camp", 
and threats of arrest for constitutionally legal activities. 

Many different views are presented, including one semi-
humorous confrontation with a group of Communists. 



In this film; 

You will witness how a multitude of New Yorkers and others are fully aware of the 
fact that 9/11 was an inside job, and how they are exposing the people behind it.

You will learn of the occult and satanic underpinnings of the ruling elite families, and how their oath to secret societies and each other makes a mockery of their counterfeit pseudo-loyalty to America and what it is supposed to stand for.

You will see the awful truth about Michael Moore, a man with basic honest 
intentions but also a man who has been carefully shepherded by the culture 
creators to pose as the orthodoxy milquetoast of the true story behind 9/11.

You will also learn the truth about Arnold Schwarzenegger, and his past, 
and why his intentions to become President should unnerve us all.


And a lot, lot more...
